.TH HSH 1 "Aughust 2021" "Holberton School"

.SH NAME
.B simple_shell
- Simple Shell for Holberton School

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./hsh

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hsh is a simple UNIX command interpreter that reads commands from standard input and executes them, simulating the behavior of the sh (/bin/sh) command interpreter (shell).

.SH OPTIONS
The hsh does not take any options for now.

.SH SEE ALSO
fork(2), free(3), getline(3), getpid(2), isatty(3), malloc(3), perror(3), sh(1), signal(2), stat(2), strtok(3), wait(2), write(2).

.SH AUTHOR
Kevin Ng'ang'a and Ola Olorunbunmi